                  "html": "<section class='bct-section bct-container'><p class='bct-section-tag'>Company Updates</p><h1 class='bct-page-title'>News and market highlights from Bright Crescent.</h1><div class='bct-grid bct-grid-3'><article class='bct-card'><div class='bct-card-media'><img src='/wp-content/themes/bright-crescent-luxe/assets/images/news-01.jpg' alt='Bright Crescent Expands Premium Appliance Procurement Network'></div><div class='bct-card-content'><p class='bct-card-meta'>Company · 2026-01-15</p><h2>Bright Crescent Expands Premium Appliance Procurement Network</h2><p>Our sourcing division now supports broader supply coverage for premium kitchen and lifestyle appliances across GCC markets.</p></div></article><article class='bct-card'><div class='bct-card-media'><img src='/wp-content/themes/bright-crescent-luxe/assets/images/news-02.jpg' alt='Crystal Collections for Hospitality and Luxury Interiors'></div><div class='bct-card-content'><p class='bct-card-meta'>Product · 2025-12-07</p><h2>Crystal Collections for Hospitality and Luxury Interiors</h2><p>We introduced curated crystal décor lines inspired by international exhibitions to support hotels, lounges, and high-end residences.</p></div></article><article class='bct-card'><div class='bct-card-media'><img src='/wp-content/themes/bright-crescent-luxe/assets/images/news-03.jpg' alt='Faster Spare Parts Availability for Cooling Systems'></div><div class='bct-card-content'><p class='bct-card-meta'>Operations · 2025-11-26</p><h2>Faster Spare Parts Availability for Cooling Systems</h2><p>Inventory optimization now improves turnaround for AC and refrigeration spare parts requested by technicians and facility teams.</p></div></article><article class='bct-card'><div class='bct-card-media'><img src='/wp-content/themes/bright-crescent-luxe/assets/images/news-04.jpg' alt='Strategic Vendor Alliances for Long-Term Quality Assurance'></div><div class='bct-card-content'><p class='bct-card-meta'>Partnership · 2025-10-13</p><h2>Strategic Vendor Alliances for Long-Term Quality Assurance</h2><p>Bright Crescent reinforces quality checks and compliance standards through strategic partner evaluation and lifecycle testing.</p></div></article></div></section>"
                },
